prompt: What are the chemical class assignments for C22H29FO4?
completion:
PREFIX os: <http://www.theworldavatar.com/ontology/ontospecies/OntoSpecies.owl#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?ChemicalClassValue 
WHERE {
    ?SpeciesIRI rdf:type os:Species ; rdfs:label ?label .

    ?SpeciesIRI ?hasIdentifier ?IdentifierIRI .
    ?IdentifierIRI  rdf:type ?Identifier ; os:value ?species .
    ?Identifier rdfs:subClassOf os:Identifier .

    FILTER( ?species = "C22H29FO4")

	?SpeciesIRI os:hasChemicalClass* ?x .
	?x ?y ?z .
	?z rdfs:subClassOf* ?ChemicalClassIRI .
	?ChemicalClassIRI rdf:type os:ChemicalClass  ; rdfs:label ?ChemicalClassValue .
}

PREFIX os: <http://www.theworldavatar.com/ontology/ontospecies/OntoSpecies.owl#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?UseValue 
WHERE {
    ?SpeciesIRI rdf:type os:Species ; rdfs:label ?label .

    ?SpeciesIRI ?hasIdentifier ?IdentifierIRI .

    ?Identifier rdfs:subClassOf os:Identifier .

    FILTER( ?species = "InChI=1S/C9H10O4/c10-7-3-1-2-6(9(7)13)4-5-8(11)12/h1-3,10,13H,4-5H2,(H,11,12)")

prompt: I'm looking for a compact summary of C(C(C(=O)O)N)O.
completion:
PREFIX os: <http://www.theworldavatar.com/ontology/ontospecies/OntoSpecies.owl#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?PropertyLabel ?PropertyNameValue ?PropertyNameUnitValue ?PropertyNameReferenceStateValue ?PropertyNameReferenceStateUnitValue
WHERE {
    ?SpeciesIRI rdf:type os:Species ; rdfs:label ?label .

    ?SpeciesIRI ?hasIdentifier ?IdentifierIRI .
    ?IdentifierIRI  rdf:type ?Identifier ; os:value ?species .
    ?Identifier rdfs:subClassOf os:Identifier .

    FILTER( ?species = "C(C(C(=O)O)N)O")

    ?SpeciesIRI ?hasPropertyName ?PropertyNameIRI .
    ?PropertyNameIRI  rdf:type ?PropertyName .
    ?PropertyName rdfs:subClassOf os:Property .
    ?PropertyNameIRI os:value ?PropertyNameValue ; os:unit ?PropertyNameUnitIRI ; os:hasProvenance ?PropertyNameProvenanceIRI . 
    ?PropertyNameUnitIRI rdfs:label ?PropertyNameUnitValue .
    OPTIONAL{?PropertyNameIRI os:hasReferenceState ?PropertyNameReferenceStateIRI . 
    ?PropertyNameReferenceStateIRI os:value ?PropertyNameReferenceStateValue ; os:unit ?PropertyNameReferenceStateUnitIRI .
    ?PropertyNameReferenceStateUnitIRI rdfs:label ?PropertyNameReferenceStateUnitValue .}
    
  	BIND(strafter(str(?PropertyName),'#') AS ?PropertyLabel)   
}

PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?IUPACNameValue ?ViscosityValue ?ViscosityUnitValue ?ViscosityReferenceStateValue ?ViscosityReferenceStateUnitValue ?VaporPressureValue ?VaporPressureUnitValue ?VaporPressureReferenceStateValue ?VaporPressureReferenceStateUnitValue
WHERE {
    ?SpeciesIRI rdf:type os:Species ; rdfs:label ?label .

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasIUPACName ?IUPACNameIRI .
    ?IUPACNameIRI os:value ?IUPACNameValue .

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasViscosity ?ViscosityIRI .
    ?ViscosityIRI os:value ?ViscosityValue ; os:unit ?ViscosityUnitIRI ; os:hasProvenance ?ViscosityProvenanceIRI . 
    ?ViscosityUnitIRI rdfs:label ?ViscosityUnitValue .
    OPTIONAL{?ViscosityIRI os:hasReferenceState ?ViscosityReferenceStateIRI .
    ?ViscosityReferenceStateIRI os:value ?ViscosityReferenceStateValue ; os:unit ?ViscosityReferenceStateUnitIRI .
    ?ViscosityReferenceStateUnitIRI rdfs:label ?ViscosityReferenceStateUnitValue .}

    FILTER(?ViscosityValue > 361)

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasVaporPressure ?VaporPressureIRI .
    ?VaporPressureIRI os:value ?VaporPressureValue ; os:unit ?VaporPressureUnitIRI ; os:hasProvenance ?VaporPressureProvenanceIRI . 
    ?VaporPressureUnitIRI rdfs:label ?VaporPressureUnitValue .
    OPTIONAL{?VaporPressureIRI os:hasReferenceState ?VaporPressureReferenceStateIRI .
    ?VaporPressureReferenceStateIRI os:value ?VaporPressureReferenceStateValue ; os:unit ?VaporPressureReferenceStateUnitIRI .
    ?VaporPressureReferenceStateUnitIRI rdfs:label ?VaporPressureReferenceStateUnitValue .}

    FILTER(?VaporPressureValue > 62)
}

prompt: What can you tell me about the  density,  autoignition temperature, and  polar surface area attributes of species recognized as N-(1-naphthyl)carboxamide?
completion:
PREFIX os: <http://www.theworldavatar.com/ontology/ontospecies/OntoSpecies.owl#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?IUPACNameValue ?DensityValue ?DensityUnitValue ?DensityReferenceStateValue ?DensityReferenceStateUnitValue ?AutoignitionTemperatureValue ?AutoignitionTemperatureUnitValue ?AutoignitionTemperatureReferenceStateValue ?AutoignitionTemperatureReferenceStateUnitValue
WHERE {
    ?SpeciesIRI rdf:type os:Species ; rdfs:label ?label .

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasIUPACName ?IUPACNameIRI .
    ?IUPACNameIRI os:value ?IUPACNameValue .

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasChemicalClass* ?x .
	?x ?y ?z .
	?z rdfs:subClassOf* ?ChemicalClassIRI .
	?ChemicalClassIRI rdf:type os:ChemicalClass  ; rdfs:label rdfs:label ?chemicalclass .

    FILTER( ?chemicalclass = "N-(1-naphthyl)carboxamide")

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasDensity ?DensityIRI .
    ?DensityIRI os:value ?DensityValue ; os:unit ?DensityUnitIRI ; os:hasProvenance ?DensityProvenanceIRI . 
    ?DensityUnitIRI rdfs:label ?DensityUnitValue .
    OPTIONAL{?DensityIRI os:hasReferenceState ?DensityReferenceStateIRI .
    ?DensityReferenceStateIRI os:value ?DensityReferenceStateValue ; os:unit ?DensityReferenceStateUnitIRI .
    ?DensityReferenceStateUnitIRI rdfs:label ?DensityReferenceStateUnitValue .}

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasAutoignitionTemperature ?AutoignitionTemperatureIRI .
    ?AutoignitionTemperatureIRI os:value ?AutoignitionTemperatureValue ; os:unit ?AutoignitionTemperatureUnitIRI ; os:hasProvenance ?AutoignitionTemperatureProvenanceIRI . 
    ?AutoignitionTemperatureUnitIRI rdfs:label ?AutoignitionTemperatureUnitValue .
    OPTIONAL{?AutoignitionTemperatureIRI os:hasReferenceState ?AutoignitionTemperatureReferenceStateIRI .
    ?AutoignitionTemperatureReferenceStateIRI os:value ?AutoignitionTemperatureReferenceStateValue ; os:unit ?AutoignitionTemperatureReferenceStateUnitIRI .
    ?AutoignitionTemperatureReferenceStateUnitIRI rdfs:label ?AutoignitionTemperatureReferenceStateUnitValue .}

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasPolarSurfaceArea ?PolarSurfaceAreaIRI .
    ?PolarSurfaceAreaIRI os:value ?PolarSurfaceAreaValue ; os:unit ?PolarSurfaceAreaUnitIRI ; os:hasProvenance ?PolarSurfaceAreaProvenanceIRI . 
    ?PolarSurfaceAreaUnitIRI rdfs:label ?PolarSurfaceAreaUnitValue .
    OPTIONAL{?PolarSurfaceAreaIRI os:hasReferenceState ?PolarSurfaceAreaReferenceStateIRI .
    ?PolarSurfaceAreaReferenceStateIRI os:value ?PolarSurfaceAreaReferenceStateValue ; os:unit ?PolarSurfaceAreaReferenceStateUnitIRI .

}

prompt: Discuss the  vapor density,  boiling point, and  bond chiral undef count particulars of species belonging to the pyridobenzodiazepine classification.
completion:
PREFIX os: <http://www.theworldavatar.com/ontology/ontospecies/OntoSpecies.owl#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?IUPACNameValue ?VaporDensityValue ?VaporDensityUnitValue ?VaporDensityReferenceStateValue ?VaporDensityReferenceStateUnitValue ?BoilingPointValue ?BoilingPointUnitValue ?BoilingPointReferenceStateValue ?BoilingPointReferenceStateUnitValue
WHERE {
    ?SpeciesIRI rdf:type os:Species ; rdfs:label ?label .

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasIUPACName ?IUPACNameIRI .
    ?IUPACNameIRI os:value ?IUPACNameValue .

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasChemicalClass* ?x .
	?x ?y ?z .
	?z rdfs:subClassOf* ?ChemicalClassIRI .
	?ChemicalClassIRI rdf:type os:ChemicalClass  ; rdfs:label rdfs:label ?chemicalclass .

    FILTER( ?chemicalclass = "pyridobenzodiazepine")

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasVaporDensity ?VaporDensityIRI .
    ?VaporDensityIRI os:value ?VaporDensityValue ; os:unit ?VaporDensityUnitIRI ; os:hasProvenance ?VaporDensityProvenanceIRI . 
    ?VaporDensityUnitIRI rdfs:label ?VaporDensityUnitValue .
    OPTIONAL{?VaporDensityIRI os:hasReferenceState ?VaporDensityReferenceStateIRI .
    ?VaporDensityReferenceStateIRI os:value ?VaporDensityReferenceStateValue ; os:unit ?VaporDensityReferenceStateUnitIRI .
    ?VaporDensityReferenceStateUnitIRI rdfs:label ?VaporDensityReferenceStateUnitValue .}

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasBoilingPoint ?BoilingPointIRI .
    ?BoilingPointIRI os:value ?BoilingPointValue ; os:unit ?BoilingPointUnitIRI ; os:hasProvenance ?BoilingPointProvenanceIRI . 
    ?BoilingPointUnitIRI rdfs:label ?BoilingPointUnitValue .
    OPTIONAL{?BoilingPointIRI os:hasReferenceState ?BoilingPointReferenceStateIRI .
    ?BoilingPointReferenceStateIRI os:value ?BoilingPointReferenceStateValue ; os:unit ?BoilingPointReferenceStateUnitIRI .
    ?BoilingPointReferenceStateUnitIRI rdfs:label ?BoilingPointReferenceStateUnitValue .}

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasBondChiralUndefCount ?BondChiralUndefCountIRI .
    ?BondChiralUndefCountIRI os:value ?BondChiralUndefCountValue ; os:unit ?BondChiralUndefCountUnitIRI ; os:hasProvenance ?BondChiralUndefCountProvenanceIRI . 
    ?BondChiralUndefCountUnitIRI rdfs:label ?BondChiralUndefCountUnitValue .
    OPTIONAL{?BondChiralUndefCountIRI os:hasReferenceState ?BondChiralUndefCountReferenceStateIRI .
    ?BondChiralUndefCountReferenceStateIRI os:value ?BondChiralUndefCountReferenceStateValue ; os:unit ?BondChiralUndefCountReferenceStateUnitIRI .
    ?BondChiralUndefCountReferenceStateUnitIRI rdfs:label ?BondChiralUndefCountReferenceStateUnitValue .}
}

PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?IUPACNameValue ?HeavyAtomCountValue ?HeavyAtomCountUnitValue ?HeavyAtomCountReferenceStateValue ?HeavyAtomCountReferenceStateUnitValue
WHERE {
    ?SpeciesIRI rdf:type os:Species ; rdfs:label ?label .

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasIUPACName ?IUPACNameIRI .
    ?IUPACNameIRI os:value ?IUPACNameValue .

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasUse ?UseIRI .
    ?UseIRI os:value ?use .

    FILTER( ?use = "antiplasmodial drug")

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasHeavyAtomCount ?HeavyAtomCountIRI .
    ?HeavyAtomCountIRI os:value ?HeavyAtomCountValue ; os:unit ?HeavyAtomCountUnitIRI ; os:hasProvenance ?HeavyAtomCountProvenanceIRI . 
    ?HeavyAtomCountUnitIRI rdfs:label ?HeavyAtomCountUnitValue .
    OPTIONAL{?HeavyAtomCountIRI os:hasReferenceState ?HeavyAtomCountReferenceStateIRI .
    ?HeavyAtomCountReferenceStateIRI os:value ?HeavyAtomCountReferenceStateValue ; os:unit ?HeavyAtomCountReferenceStateUnitIRI .
    ?HeavyAtomCountReferenceStateUnitIRI rdfs:label ?HeavyAtomCountReferenceStateUnitValue .}

    FILTER(?HeavyAtomCountValue > 395 && ?HeavyAtomCountValue < 880)
}

    ?SpeciesIRI ?hasIdentifier ?IdentifierIRI .
    ?IdentifierIRI  rdf:type ?Identifier ; os:value ?species .
    ?Identifier rdfs:subClassOf os:Identifier .

    FILTER( ?species = "InChI=1S/C6H12N2O3/c1-3(7)5(9)8-4(2)6(10)11/h3-4H,7H2,1-2H3,(H,8,9)(H,10,11)")

    ?HeatOfCombustionReferenceStateIRI os:value ?HeatOfCombustionReferenceStateValue ; os:unit ?HeatOfCombustionReferenceStateUnitIRI .
    ?HeatOfCombustionReferenceStateUnitIRI rdfs:label ?HeatOfCombustionReferenceStateUnitValue .}

    ?StandardEnthalpyOfFormationUnitIRI rdfs:label ?StandardEnthalpyOfFormationUnitValue .
    OPTIONAL{?StandardEnthalpyOfFormationIRI os:hasReferenceState ?StandardEnthalpyOfFormationReferenceStateIRI .
    ?StandardEnthalpyOfFormationReferenceStateIRI os:value ?StandardEnthalpyOfFormationReferenceStateValue ; os:unit ?StandardEnthalpyOfFormationReferenceStateUnitIRI .

prompt: What can you tell me about the  bond chiral def count,  solubility, and  caco2 permeability attributes of species recognized as boron atom?
completion:
PREFIX os: <http://www.theworldavatar.com/ontology/ontospecies/OntoSpecies.owl#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?IUPACNameValue ?BondChiralDefCountValue ?BondChiralDefCountUnitValue ?BondChiralDefCountReferenceStateValue ?BondChiralDefCountReferenceStateUnitValue ?SolubilityValue ?SolubilityUnitValue ?SolubilityReferenceStateValue ?SolubilityReferenceStateUnitValue
WHERE {
    ?SpeciesIRI rdf:type os:Species ; rdfs:label ?label .

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasIUPACName ?IUPACNameIRI .
    ?IUPACNameIRI os:value ?IUPACNameValue .

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasChemicalClass* ?x .
	?x ?y ?z .
	?z rdfs:subClassOf* ?ChemicalClassIRI .
	?ChemicalClassIRI rdf:type os:ChemicalClass  ; rdfs:label rdfs:label ?chemicalclass .

    FILTER( ?chemicalclass = "boron atom")

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasBondChiralDefCount ?BondChiralDefCountIRI .
    ?BondChiralDefCountIRI os:value ?BondChiralDefCountValue ; os:unit ?BondChiralDefCountUnitIRI ; os:hasProvenance ?BondChiralDefCountProvenanceIRI . 
    ?BondChiralDefCountUnitIRI rdfs:label ?BondChiralDefCountUnitValue .
    OPTIONAL{?BondChiralDefCountIRI os:hasReferenceState ?BondChiralDefCountReferenceStateIRI .
    ?BondChiralDefCountReferenceStateIRI os:value ?BondChiralDefCountReferenceStateValue ; os:unit ?BondChiralDefCountReferenceStateUnitIRI .
    ?BondChiralDefCountReferenceStateUnitIRI rdfs:label ?BondChiralDefCountReferenceStateUnitValue .}

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasSolubility ?SolubilityIRI .
    ?SolubilityIRI os:value ?SolubilityValue ; os:unit ?SolubilityUnitIRI ; os:hasProvenance ?SolubilityProvenanceIRI . 
    ?SolubilityUnitIRI rdfs:label ?SolubilityUnitValue .
    OPTIONAL{?SolubilityIRI os:hasReferenceState ?SolubilityReferenceStateIRI .
    ?SolubilityReferenceStateIRI os:value ?SolubilityReferenceStateValue ; os:unit ?SolubilityReferenceStateUnitIRI .
    ?SolubilityReferenceStateUnitIRI rdfs:label ?SolubilityReferenceStateUnitValue .}

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasCaco2Permeability ?Caco2PermeabilityIRI .
    ?Caco2PermeabilityIRI os:value ?Caco2PermeabilityValue ; os:unit ?Caco2PermeabilityUnitIRI ; os:hasProvenance ?Caco2PermeabilityProvenanceIRI . 
    ?Caco2PermeabilityUnitIRI rdfs:label ?Caco2PermeabilityUnitValue .
    OPTIONAL{?Caco2PermeabilityIRI os:hasReferenceState ?Caco2PermeabilityReferenceStateIRI .
    ?Caco2PermeabilityReferenceStateIRI os:value ?Caco2PermeabilityReferenceStateValue ; os:unit ?Caco2PermeabilityReferenceStateUnitIRI .
    ?Caco2PermeabilityReferenceStateUnitIRI rdfs:label ?Caco2PermeabilityReferenceStateUnitValue .}
}

prompt: What's the  in ch i that defines C15H11ClN2O?
completion:
PREFIX os: <http://www.theworldavatar.com/ontology/ontospecies/OntoSpecies.owl#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?label ?InChIValue
WHERE {
    ?SpeciesIRI rdf:type os:Species ; rdfs:label ?label .

    ?SpeciesIRI ?hasIdentifier ?IdentifierIRI .
    ?IdentifierIRI  rdf:type ?Identifier ; os:value ?species .
    ?Identifier rdfs:subClassOf os:Identifier .

    FILTER( ?species = "C15H11ClN2O")

    ?SpeciesIRI os:hasInChI ?InChIIRI .
    ?InChIIRI os:value ?InChIValue .
}
